item.title: A Loan Bazaar Where You Can Literally Buy Loans for Pennies - FOLIOfn
item.description:
A Loan Bazaar Where You Can Literally Buy Loans for Pennies - FOLIOfn

Welcome to the true marketplace where you can trade debt on any level you like You haven't experienced marketplace lending until you've entered the world of FOLIOfn. Operating as a secondary market for Lending Club and Prosper investors, the platform offers more than just liquidity for holders of 3-5 year consumer debt-backed notes.
